<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'pages/index', media: 'all' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag 'pages/index', :defer => "defer" %>

<div class="main">
  <div class="container panel hidden" id="hero">
    <div class="five columns" id="hero-content">
      <h3>introducing</h3>
      <h1 class="h-lg">unlosable glasses</h1>
      <h2>Beautifully handmade glasses you won't lose.</h2>
      <a href="/unlosable-glasses"><button id="learn-more" class="sm-btn alternate tz-track" data-category="index" data-event="learn-more-click">learn more &nbsp; &rarr;</button></a>
    </div>

    <div class="seven columns" id="hero-image">
      <a href="/unlosable-glasses"><%= image_tag 'glasses/docked-overhead.jpg' %></a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container"><hr/></div>
  <div class="panel" id="press">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="six columns">
        <a href="/press#afr-0"><%= image_tag 'press/afr_logo.png', id: 'article-1-logo' %></a>
        <a href="/press#afr-0"><h1>Impossible to lose</h1></a>
        <p>The glasses are balanced, comfortable and - in the eyes of this writer, at least - stylish. And the locator app, which is loaded onto your smartphone at the time of purchase, is clean and intuitive...</p>
      </div>
      <div class="six columns">
        <a href="/press#smh-0"><%= image_tag 'press/smh_logo.png', id: 'article-2-logo' %></a>
        <a href="/press#smh-0"><h1>Never lose your glasses again</h1></a>
        <p>When Allen Liao was still at university he borrowed a friend's expensive sunglasses and lost them. "He wasn't very happy with me so that's how it all started," Liao says.</p>
        <p id="more-press"><a href="/press">Read more...</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="two-panels">
    <a href="/retail">
      <div id="store">
        <div class="bg photo"></div>
        <div class="bg gradient"></div>
        <div class="content">sydney store</div>
      </div>
    </a>
    <a href="/gallery">
      <div id="gallery">
        <div class="bg photo"></div>
        <div class="bg gradient"></div>
        <div class="content">gallery</div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
